privateJob.title: Shell Team Lead Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for Various vacancies in Chennai
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • Team Lead

Description:

Shell has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of Team Lead. If you are finding jobs in Chennai then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by Shell can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles and responsibilities are given below. Shell is dealing with oil products products. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies has released.

Selection Process:

  • Personal Interview 

Role and responsibility:

  • Assist the team to adhere to Company and Project HSE Goals and ensure subcontractors are included in all HSE related initiatives.
  • Support personal safety within the team and the wellbeing of co-workers by regularly addressing HSE behavior.
  • Risk Management
  • These are some of the roles and responsibilities for one post. You should check for each post shown in apply now link

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for Shell job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the Engineering Degree from a recognized university to apply for the application Shell Team Lead Recruitment 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • You must have knowledge of Risk Management Analyst, Excellent analytical, oral and written communication skills.
  • Check it out on apply now link shown above.

Pay scale info. :

  • The Pay scale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Aadhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Shell Team Lead Recruitment 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Shell Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

  • Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here
  • First of all, read the Shell Team Lead Recruitment 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website @shell.in
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
